                <p>The Office of Scholarships assists current UIC undergraduate and professional students in searching and applying for campus scholarships opportunities. This office can also assist with external opportunities for undergraduate and professional tuition and housing scholarships, but nationally competitive scholarships and fellowships are managed by the Office of External Fellowships.</p>

            </div>
            </div>

    <div class="component-tab-group__tabs">
      <div class="tab-group">
