</div>
</dd>
<dt class="component-accordion__title" role="heading" aria-level="4"><button id="tab-sectionID-8-4" class="component-accordion__button js-toggle-acc" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panel-sectionID-8-4">Martin Luther King Jr. Scholarship</button></dt>
<dd id="panel-sectionID-8-4" class="component-accordion__content component-accordion__content--collapsed" role="region" aria-labelledby="tab-sectionID-8-4">
<div class="component-accordion__content-wrapper">
<div class="components">
<div class="component">
<div class="component-text-block">
<p>For sophomores, juniors and graduate students in any major, $2000 for undergraduates, or $5000 for graduates toward continuing studies.</p>
<ul>
<li>Deadline: March</li>
<li>Website: <strong><a href="http://vcsa.uic.edu/scholarships/dr-martin-scholarship/">http://vcsa.uic.edu/scholarships/dr-martin-scholarship/</a><br />
</strong></li>
</ul>
