  <div class="component-text-block">
    <h2 class="invisible">.</h2>
  
  
  <p>SnAP is UIC’s internal scholarship information system. If you are a UIC student, you can <a href="https://uic.academicworks.com/users/sign_in"><strong>log in</strong></a> using your UIC netid and password and SnAP will show you a list of scholarships that you qualify, based on a number of criteria, including major, financial aid status, etc.</p>



  
