<li>Eligibility: U.S. citizens; seniors or recent graduates</li>
<li>UIC Deadline: Mid-April</li>
<li>Website: <strong><a href="https://www.us-irelandalliance.org/mitchellscholarship" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.us-irelandalliance.org/mitchellscholarship</a></strong></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</dd>
<dt class="component-accordion__title" role="heading" aria-level="4"><button id="tab-sectionID-7-4" class="component-accordion__button js-toggle-acc" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panel-sectionID-7-4">Rhodes Scholarships</button></dt>
<dd id="panel-sectionID-7-4" class="component-accordion__content component-accordion__content--collapsed" role="region" aria-labelledby="tab-sectionID-7-4">
<div class="component-accordion__content-wrapper">
<div class="components">
<div class="component">
<div class="component-text-block">
<p>For outstanding students with a 3.7 gpa or higher, research, service, leadership and vision for making a difference; offers graduate study at Oxford University for 1-2 years. UIC starts to prepare candidates in the spring for fall deadlines.</p>
<ul>
<li>Eligibility: U.S. citizens; seniors or recent graduates (other countries also have Rhodes offerings).</li>
<li>UIC Deadline: Mid-April</li>
<li>Website: <strong><a href="http://www.rhodesscholar.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.rhodesscholar.org/</a></strong></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</div>



  
</div>

  
</section>

    

</div>
            </div>
          <div
              class="tab-group__tabpanel"
              tabindex="0"
              role="tabpanel"
              id="panel-tabID-4-4"
              aria-labelledby="tab-tabID-4-4">

              <div class="components">
      
      

<section class="component  ">

  
  <div class="component-text-block">
    <h2 class="invisible">.</h2>
  
  
  <p>The Office of External Fellowships is located in 802 University Hall. You may contact them in person, via phone, or e-mail. In addition, you may join their mailing list at <a href="http://oef.uic.edu/about/join-mailing-list/">uic.edu/about/join-mailing-list/</a>.</p>
<p>OEF Contact Information</p>
<ul>
<li>(312)355-3380</li>
<li><a href="mailto:oef@uic.edu">oef@uic.edu</a></li>
</ul>



  
</div>

  
</section>

    

